snippet.title: Putt-Putt Saves the Zoo - Official Trailer | PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Putt-Putt Saves the Zoo is coming to PS4 on November 3rd!

Today's the grand opening of the Cartown Zoo, and there's still so much to do: zoo chow is running low, and all the baby animals are missing.

#ps4games #ps4
